CBRE are pleased to present an opportunity to acquire 2Ha* of Special Use zoned waterfront land incorporating transportable office buildings, workshops, jetty and hardstand.

This property represents one of only 6 sites that are owned freehold (excluding LandCorp) adjacent to the ocean in the main shipbuilding and marine related precinct in Western Australia.

IMPROVEMENTS
- Office 234sqm*
- Transportable next to office 36sqm*
- Transportable on steel framed platform 36sqm*
- Transportable on ground under platform 36sqm*
- General purpose shed 79sqm*
- Main fabrication workshop inclusive of toilets 915sqm*
- Lunchroom to fabrication 25sqm*
- Compressor shelter 23sqm*
- Mezzanine transportable office in fabrication shed 18sqm*
- Site transportable toilet 13sqm*
- Transportable lunchroom next to fabrication shed 36sqm*
- Transportable lunchroom/first aid next to fabrication shed 30sqm*

*approx

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to offer 21 Egmont Road, Henderson located within the Australian Marine Complex for lease.

The warehouse has a truss height of between 7m* and
10m*. The yard is fully bitumen and has two (2) crossovers for ease of truck access.

The office is carpeted/air-conditioned and ready to
occupy.

This property will suit a number of different uses.
The owners will offer attractive lease terms for the right tenant.


*approx

Located in the heart of The Australian Marine Complex,this superb facility will be for lease soon.

Currently occupied by Tyco Hydraulic Motion & Control,this building is full fitted with quality office accomodation,substantial warehouse/workshop and excellent truck access with laydown areas.The office area is 335 sqm and has a factory/warehouse of 1410 sqm approx.Yard area is to the side and rear of this property.

Superb on-site parking enhances this secure building.

For an inspection,please contact Geoff Fraser on 0413 624 000

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: "Perfect Industrial Headquarters in Henderson for lease"

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to present to the market 32 Stuart Drive, Henderson for sale by an Offers Invited campaign closing Wednesday 23rd September 2015 at 4.00pm WST.

The property is uniquely located within the Henderson Industrial Estate and more specifically the Australian Marine Complex (AMC), a specialist precinct designed to cater for those industries that service the marine, oil and gas and resource sectors.

Key attributes :

- A 2,400sqm* site just near the corner of Stuart Drive and Cockburn Road
- Modern 1,346sqm* improvements
- 34 kilometres* from the Perth CBD and 17 kilometres* from Fremantle Port
- Zoned Industrial under the Metropolitan region Scheme and "Special Use 2-Development Area 15" under the City of Cockburn's Town Planning Scheme
- Accessible via some of Perth's main arterial roads including the "High Wide Load" corridor

*approx
